title: Styles Of Beyond - Razor Tag: Key Cuts EP
description:
Razor Tag: Key Cuts EP is a selected assortment of tracks off the first official full-length Styles Of Beyond Mixtape, Razor Tag. It was released only in digital Mp3 format exclusively on http://www.HipHopSite.com/, and contains tracks off the original mixtape, without any shoutouts, drops, sound effects, or transitions of any kind.

-It&#039;s Us - 2:27

-Live At The BBQ (Featuring Demigodz) - 3:05
-Godz In Da Front (Featuring Demigodz) - 4:49
-Savin&#039; L.A. (Featuring Bishop Lamont) - 4:08
